+
+## 1. Scan the reference library
 
 ```
-+-------------+       +-----------------+       +------------------------+
-| DEDUPE_DIR |  -->  | gather metadata  |  -->  | pick preferred version |
-+-------------+       +-----------------+       +------------------------+
-                                              | library <= healthiest |
-                                              +-----------+------------+
-                                                          |
-                                                          v
-                                        +------------------------------------+
-                                        | move/delete/swap + prune empties   |
-                                        +------------------------------------+
